---
description: Safety constraints for desktop automation
globs:
  - modules/hooks.py
  - scripts/**/*
alwaysApply: false
---

- **Never run sudo** from hooks or on keypress. Keep privileged tasks as manual shell commands.
- Avoid writing secrets into tracked files. Use environment variables and `.gitignore`.
- Review any command that manipulates power/session (`systemctl suspend`, `loginctl lock-session`) before binding.
